{"tid":1362164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩睇完icac個post有少少野想講","createTime":"2019-07-24T19:39:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T20:34:07.000Z","uid":259162,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f5931cd0c5d47cffe2ae7d93fbdb14bc335e6223","tid":1362164,"uid":259162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T19:39:08.000Z","msg":"唔好再對人冷嘲熱諷，對於icac做唔到野大家都好嬲，係絕對理解! <br />\n<br />\n雖然佢只有一個人，雖然可能佢做唔到野，但係佢好可能就係個頭! 之後就越黎越多人加入<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好鬧走人啊!<br />\n<br />\n例如: icac原來再係度?<br />\n<br />\n試下講: 多謝你既支持! 但老實講市民唔係好感受到icac做到野. 有冇辦法建議可以令你地做到野，或者多啲icac既人支持啊?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"> 大家謹記日本社運既教訓啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"9d877cb0dbb869203c05b231d6ab067e4a5a55a0","tid":1362164,"uid":259162,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T19:43:36.000Z","msg":"就算有黑警加入都係，回頭是岸就係同路人! 大家要團結，同埋鼓吹回頭是岸既風氣啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed9abc628dcc8d2a949387e9eb0bfd7f4bedcd0","tid":1362164,"uid":259162,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T19:56:31.000Z","msg":"大家要製造到個氛圍比黑警倒戈先得，連icac都咁講野，如果我係黑警，我都揀為左糧繼續打市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb56385ea601341c112976ebadd6ffa90c3f88e5","tid":1362164,"uid":259162,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T19:57:48.000Z","msg":"大家要團結啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，一個也不少，多一個就好多，團結唔係得個講。"},{"pid":"51694bba5f73600d32718b4e68a003d33c17f0a1","tid":1362164,"uid":259162,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T19:59:37.000Z","msg":"可能你會覺得邊有人個玻璃心，但問心大家都知玻璃心既人根本唔係少數(包括我)。<br />\n一個都唔少啊，大家要創造良好氛圍啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4cf52c10d7bdc2bcb5bcaec2